。 BBC为你编撰详尽对照表，方便使用。</p><time dateTime="2019-07-08" class="StyledTimestamp-um718p-0 goWQjX">2019年7月8日</time></div></div></li></ul></section><section role="region" aria-labelledby="Showcase-5" class="StyledSection-sc-1x9qbiu-0 hNdEyC"><div class="SectionLabelWrapper-sc-1x4gwjz-1 hsirkD"><div class="Bar-sc-1x4gwjz-0 kXOyLn"></div><h2 class="Heading-sc-1x4gwjz-2 eZofTG"><span class="FlexColumn-wx5kdp-0 dgpsiS"><span class="FlexRow-wx5kdp-2 dVBNyZ"><span dir="ltr" id="Showcase-5" class="Title-wx5kdp-4 eTPfkr">浏览协助</span></span></span></h2></div><div class="SpacingDiv-sc-1x9qbiu-2 jduYfx"><div class="StoryPromoWrapper-sc-1dvfmi3-0 hpUEiZ"><div dir="ltr" class="ImageGridItem-sc-1xk56cj-0 dGiaGH"><div class="ImageContentsWrapper-sc-1dvfmi3-1 cinwNl"><div class="ImagePlaceholder-sc-11u25v2-0 _StyledImagePlaceholder-gu1fm2-0 kvTWeV"><div class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div><div class="ImageOverlayWrapper-sc-1dvfmi3-2 cWJDXG"></div></div></div><div dir="ltr" class="TextGridItem-sc-1lkbq5i-0 gAqLWy"><h3 class="Headline-sc-1dvfmi3-3 dTkvXH"><a href="http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/institutional/2013/02/130215_proxy_notice.shtml" class="Link-sc-1dvfmi3-5 jeUMCT">代理服务器和翻墙软件</a></h3><p class="Summary-sc-1dvfmi3-4 xpXpq">如你在登录BBC中文网时遭遇困难，请试用代理服务器。</p><time dateTime="2016-12-06" class="StyledTimestamp-um718p-0 goWQjX">2016年12月6日</time></div></div></div></section></div></main><footer role="contentinfo"><div class="Banner-m3awbo-1 gpxnCd"><div class="SvgWrapper-m3awbo-0 dPXtDJ"><a href="/zhongwen" class="StyledLink-m3awbo-2 kwiuCU"><svg height="24" viewBox="0 0 217.3 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" class="BrandSvg-m3awbo-3 ldeDeZ"><g fill-rule="evenodd" stroke="#000" stroke-width=".335" style="stroke:#fff"><path d="M76.73.28v21.85H53.51V.28zm-4.62 14.58l-.37.23a10.85 10.85 0 0 1-5.53 1.69c-3.8 0-6.31-2.27-6.32-5.55s2.62-5.58 6.22-5.59a10.93 10.93 0 0 1 5.47 1.56l.36.2V4.47l-.16-.06a15.06 15.06 0 0 0-5.65-1.27 9.62 9.62 0 0 0-6.53 2.34 